Description: Bridge between D-Bus and MQTT
 dbus-mqtt-bridge is a service that bidirectionally bridges D-Bus signals
 and method calls with MQTT topics and messages. This allows D-Bus services
 to communicate with MQTT-based systems and vice versa.
 .
 Features:
  * Forward D-Bus signals to MQTT topics
  * Trigger D-Bus method calls from MQTT messages
  * Support for both system and session bus
  * Configurable via YAML
  * Runs as unprivileged system user
  * Comprehensive systemd integration
 .
 This package includes the main service, configuration examples, and
 D-Bus policy templates.